Global Armchairs Market Insights
Armchairs Market size was valued at USD 8.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 11.2 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 4.1% from 2024 to 2030.

Armchairs Market Overview
The global armchairs market was valued at USD 10.02 billion in 2024 and is expected to grow at a CAGR of 6.5% from 2024 to 2032. This growth is driven by an increasing demand for comfortable, stylish, and functional furniture in residential, commercial, and hospitality sectors. The market is influenced by consumer preferences for ergonomic designs, eco-friendly materials, and multi-functional furniture, especially in urbanized regions. Rising disposable incomes, urbanization, and a shift towards home-office setups are contributing to the demand for premium and customized armchairs.

